{"timestamp": "2025-10-29T12:35:05.690288", "level": "INFO", "name": "chatbot_app", "message": "Executing query: -- This query assumes the existence of a 'product_category' table and a linking column in the 'product' table.\n-- The provided schema for the 'product' table does not contain category information.\n-- Please replace 'product_category', 'category_sid', and 'category_name' with your actual schema names.\nSELECT\n  p.plu, -- Product Lookup Code (PLU)\n  p.plu_name, -- Nama produk\n  pc.category_name -- Nama kategori (diasumsikan dari tabel 'product_category')\nFROM\n  product AS p\n  -- Menggunakan LEFT JOIN untuk memastikan semua produk ditampilkan, bahkan jika kategori tidak ada\n  -- The JOIN operation is based on an assumed schema structure where 'product' has a 'category_sid' foreign key.\nLEFT JOIN\n  product_category AS pc ON p.category_sid = pc.category_sid\n-- Batasi jumlah hasil yang ditampilkan untuk menjaga performa\nLIMIT 100;...", "app": "chatbot_app", "environment": "development"}
