{"timestamp": "2025-10-30T06:47:29.129165", "level": "INFO", "name": "chatbot_app", "message": "   Schema info retrieved: \n CREATE TABLE store_master (\n  store_sid INTEGER NOT NULL,\n  code VARCHAR(20),\n  name VARCHAR(50),\n  branch_sid INTEGER,\n  PRIMARY KEY (store_sid)\n)\n\n/* Table: store_master\nDescription: Master table untuk toko/outlet. Setiap toko belongs to satu cabang. Contains flagship stores dan regular outlets.\n\nColumns:\n  - store_sid (integer): Primary key - Unique identifier untuk toko\n  - code (character varying(20)): Kode toko (e.g., TLPC, TCWS, TPLG) - Unique identifier untuk business operations. Case-sensitive untuk exact match.\n  - name (character varying(50)): Nama lengkap toko (e.g., FS LIPPO CIKARANG, FLAGSHIP CIPUTRA WORLD) - Use ILIKE for search\n  - branch_sid (integer): Foreign key - branch.branch_sid - Cabang yang mengelola toko ini\n*/\n\n/*\n9369\tTALS\tSS ALAM SUTERA\t183 rows from store_master table:\nstore_sid\tcode\tname\tbranch_sid\n\n7905\tTPLG\tFS PALEMBANG\t23 rows from store_master table:\nstore_sid\tcode\tname\tbranch_sid\n\n8423\tTSGS\tSS SPBU GADING SERPONG\t18\n*/\n\nCREATE TABLE branch (\n  branch_sid INTEGER NOT NULL,\n  code VARCHAR(20),\n  name VARCHAR(50),\n  PRIMARY KEY (branch_sid)\n)\n\n/* Table: branch\nDescription: Master table untuk cabang/region. Setiap cabang mengelola beberapa toko. Data range: Oct 2024 - Sep 2025.\n\nColumns:\n  - branch_sid (integer): Primary key - Unique identifier untuk cabang\n  - code (character varying(20)): Kode cabang (e.g., GJKT TBSD) - Unique identifier untuk business operations\n  - name (character varying(50)): Nama lengkap cabang (e.g., CENTRAL KITCHEN ANCOL, FLAGSHIP BSD)\n*/\n\n/*\n18\tTBSD\tFLAGHSHIP BSD3 rows from branch table:\nbranch_sid\tcode\tname\n\n2\tGJKT\tCENTRAL KITCHEN ANCOL\n*/)", "app": "chatbot_app", "environment": "development"}
{"timestamp": "2025-10-30T06:47:29.130740", "level": "INFO", "name": "chatbot_app", "message": "\u270d\ufe0f Step 3: Generating SQL (iteration 1)", "app": "chatbot_app", "environment": "development"}
{"timestamp": "2025-10-30T06:47:29.136568", "level": "INFO", "name": "chatbot_app", "message": "[PROMPT] Generate Query Node: You are a PostgreSQL expert for a donut shop business intelligence system.\n\nQuestion: Berapa jumlah toko dengan nama MISTER DONUT?\n\nDatabase Schema:\nCREATE TABLE store_master (\n  store_sid INTEGER NOT NULL,\n  code VARCHAR(20),\n  name VARCHAR(50),\n  branch_sid INTEGER,\n  PRIMARY KEY (store_sid)\n)\n\n/* Table: store_master\nDescription: Master table untuk toko/outlet. Setiap toko belongs to satu cabang. Contains flagship stores dan regular outlets.\n\nColumns:\n  - store_sid (integer): Primary key - Unique identifier untuk toko\n  - code (character varying(20)): Kode toko (e.g., TLPC, TCWS, TPLG) - Unique identifier untuk business operations. Case-sensitive untuk exact match.\n  - name (character varying(50)): Nama lengkap toko (e.g., FS LIPPO CIKARANG, FLAGSHIP CIPUTRA WORLD) - Use ILIKE for search\n  - branch_sid (integer): Foreign key - branch.branch_sid - Cabang yang mengelola toko ini\n*/\n\n/*\n9369\tTALS\tSS ALAM SUTERA\t183 rows from store_master table:\nstore_sid\tcode\tname\tbranch_sid\n\n7905\tTPLG\tFS PALEMBANG\t23 rows from store_master table:\nstore_sid\tcode\tname\tbranch_sid\n\n8423\tTSGS\tSS SPBU GADING SERPONG\t18\n*/\n\nCREATE TABLE branch (\n  branch_sid INTEGER NOT NULL,\n  code VARCHAR(20),\n  name VARCHAR(50),\n  PRIMARY KEY (branch_sid)\n)\n\n/* Table: branch\nDescription: Master table untuk cabang/region. Setiap cabang mengelola beberapa toko. Data range: Oct 2024 - Sep 2025.\n\nColumns:\n  - branch_sid (integer): Primary key - Unique identifier untuk cabang\n  - code (character varying(20)): Kode cabang (e.g., GJKT TBSD) - Unique identifier untuk business operations\n  - name (character varying(50)): Nama lengkap cabang (e.g., CENTRAL KITCHEN ANCOL, FLAGSHIP BSD)\n*/\n\n/*\n18\tTBSD\tFLAGHSHIP BSD3 rows from branch table:\nbranch_sid\tcode\tname\n\n2\tGJKT\tCENTRAL KITCHEN ANCOL\n*/\n\nCRITICAL RULES:\n1. ALWAYS add LIMIT clause (default 100, or 10-20 for rankings) unless query has aggregation without GROUP BY\n2. NEVER use SELECT * - always specify columns explicitly\n3. Add SQL comments (--) to explain your logic\n4. For sales queries with qty_sales/rp_sales: MUST filter (qty_sales > 0 OR rp_sales > 0)\n\nBEST PRACTICES:\n- Use ILIKE for case-insensitive text search\n- Use CAST(date AS DATE) for date comparisons\n- Add date filters only when question asks about specific time period\n- For transaction counts: COUNT(DISTINCT NULLIF(sales_code, ''))\n\nDate handling:\n- Today: CURRENT_DATE\n- Yesterday: CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 day'\n- Last N days: CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL 'N days'\n- This month: DATE_TRUNC('month', CURRENT_DATE)\n\n\n\nGenerate ONLY the SQL query (no explanation, no markdown).\nAdd -- comments in the SQL to explain each step.", "app": "chatbot_app", "environment": "development"}
